description:
Danny recaps this week's THRILLING/AMAZING episode of The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which featured a cooking class gone wrong, Jennie making yogurt, and the Beauty Lab & Laser parking lot fiasco we've been waiting for!! Danny also touches on The Real Housewives of Potomac reunion, Garfield casting, granola options, and SO MUCH more!!


RHOP: 46:25ish
